  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The birds have caught your attention, their noise is tormenting—it’s time to scare them away!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Just a Little Purr suit</i> is a turn-based strategy puzzle game. <strong>65 handcrafted levels</strong>,<i> </i>a fun adventure designed for the whole family! With no time limit, you can choose a direction and use cards to perform an available action within the level, such as:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Common movement cards:</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cards that move the kitten forward by slots.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377720/extras/527ea8828a8815ae6f3f196b69989469.poster.avif?t=1767019833\" width=780 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377720/extras/527ea8828a8815ae6f3f196b69989469.webm?t=1767019833\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377720/extras/527ea8828a8815ae6f3f196b69989469.mp4?t=1767019833\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If in doubt, <strong>you can undo the action.</strong> The card will return to its initial position. Explore different solutions to the challenge!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Special Cannon Card:</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Allows you to choose the direction to launch the kitten, propelling it by the distance specified on the card. Remember, every cat always lands on its feet.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377720/extras/1048f1a872bdf25e19a21ca222d703ae.poster.avif?t=1767019833\" width=780 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377720/extras/1048f1a872bdf25e19a21ca222d703ae.webm?t=1767019833\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377720/extras/1048f1a872bdf25e19a21ca222d703ae.mp4?t=1767019833\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Special Trampoline Card:</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The direction cannot be chosen, but you can determine the distance. However, it will always move forward.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377720/extras/263f0876160be376d2e425cf46c8f345.poster.avif?t=1767019833\" width=780 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377720/extras/263f0876160be376d2e425cf46c8f345.webm?t=1767019833\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377720/extras/263f0876160be376d2e425cf46c8f345.mp4?t=1767019833\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Special Portal Card:</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some myths say cats travel between mysterious universes. In <i>Little Purrsuit</i>, this myth is true. The portal will always appear ahead of the kitten, allowing it to pass from one portal to another.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377720/extras/466c71e5ffbf96c900e93ee42a8f0061.poster.avif?t=1767019833\" width=780 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377720/extras/466c71e5ffbf96c900e93ee42a8f0061.webm?t=1767019833\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377720/extras/466c71e5ffbf96c900e93ee42a8f0061.mp4?t=1767019833\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Special Create new Platform Card:</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Creates a new platform to aid in navigation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377720/extras/4c51e1443cd6ae6942bd89172409e69e.poster.avif?t=1767019833\" width=780 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377720/extras/4c51e1443cd6ae6942bd89172409e69e.webm?t=1767019833\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377720/extras/4c51e1443cd6ae6942bd89172409e69e.mp4?t=1767019833\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The environment will challenge you! Boosters and totems can either help or hinder you by changing your position.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377720/extras/8879ce94d090a5abb4d7eba260aa89f0.poster.avif?t=1767019833\" width=780 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377720/extras/8879ce94d090a5abb4d7eba260aa89f0.webm?t=1767019833\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377720/extras/8879ce94d090a5abb4d7eba260aa89f0.mp4?t=1767019833\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The birds have caught your attention, their noise is tormenting—it’s time to scare them away!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Just a Little Purr suit</i> is a turn-based strategy puzzle game. <strong>65 handcrafted levels</strong>,<i> </i>a fun adventure designed for the whole family! With no time limit, you can choose a direction and use cards to perform an available action within the level, such as:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Common movement cards:</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cards that move the kitten forward by slots.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377720/extras/527ea8828a8815ae6f3f196b69989469.poster.avif?t=1767019833\" width=780 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377720/extras/527ea8828a8815ae6f3f196b69989469.webm?t=1767019833\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377720/extras/527ea8828a8815ae6f3f196b69989469.mp4?t=1767019833\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If in doubt, <strong>you can undo the action.</strong> The card will return to its initial position. Explore different solutions to the challenge!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Special Cannon Card:</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Allows you to choose the direction to launch the kitten, propelling it by the distance specified on the card. Remember, every cat always lands on its feet.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377720/extras/1048f1a872bdf25e19a21ca222d703ae.poster.avif?t=1767019833\" width=780 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377720/extras/1048f1a872bdf25e19a21ca222d703ae.webm?t=1767019833\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377720/extras/1048f1a872bdf25e19a21ca222d703ae.mp4?t=1767019833\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Special Trampoline Card:</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The direction cannot be chosen, but you can determine the distance. However, it will always move forward.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377720/extras/263f0876160be376d2e425cf46c8f345.poster.avif?t=1767019833\" width=780 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377720/extras/263f0876160be376d2e425cf46c8f345.webm?t=1767019833\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377720/extras/263f0876160be376d2e425cf46c8f345.mp4?t=1767019833\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Special Portal Card:</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some myths say cats travel between mysterious universes. In <i>Little Purrsuit</i>, this myth is true. The portal will always appear ahead of the kitten, allowing it to pass from one portal to another.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377720/extras/466c71e5ffbf96c900e93ee42a8f0061.poster.avif?t=1767019833\" width=780 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377720/extras/466c71e5ffbf96c900e93ee42a8f006